videos.headline: Robinson's 71-yard gain sets up Mitchell's TD
videos.description: Hendon Hooker throws to Tayvion Robinson, who is stopped just short of the end zone for a 71-yard gain. James Mitchell runs in a touchdown on the next play.

videos.headline: Turner leaps up to haul in Hooker's TD pass
videos.description: Hendon Hooker throws to Tre Turner, who leaps in the air to complete a three-yard touchdown.
